    "**Mitigating Limitations** To mitigate these limitations, I: 1.",
    "**Stay Current with Continuing Education**: I regularly attend conferences, workshops, and online courses to stay up-to-date with the latest developments in neurosurgery. 2.",
    "**Collaborate with Colleagues**: I work with a multidisciplinary team of healthcare professionals to ensure that my patients receive comprehensive care. 3.",
    "**Seek Consultation**: When faced with complex or unusual cases, I seek consultation with other experts to ensure that my patients receive the best possible care. 4.",
    "**Engage in Quality Improvement**: I participate in quality improvement initiatives to identify areas for improvement and optimize patient outcomes.By acknowledging the limitations of my knowledge and expertise, I can provide the best possible care for my patients while also recognizing the importance of ongoing learning and collaboration."
